Class DisplaySettings

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • userinterface.graph.DisplaySettings
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable, SettingOwner

    public class DisplaySettings
extends java.util.Observable
implements SettingOwner
    Representation of the display settings of a Graph. The settings are propagated to the JFreeChart library.
